      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my reliable ride that's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in great shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for anyone looking for a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. It runs super smoothly and looks fantastic inside and out. I'm honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know it'll make its next owner very happy! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
