    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 naturally aspirated inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This driver-focused example utilizes a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and professional reinforcement of the rear subframe to maintain structural chassis integrity. The suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings, ensuring precise turn-in and communicative feedback through the steering rack. While exhibiting minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the powertrain remains potent, delivering linear acceleration up to its 8,000 RPM redline.",
      "price": 34500.0,
